<META NAME="description" CONTENT="The Kamoun Lab at The Sainsbury
Laboratory: An inordinate fondness for effectors. The laboratory of
Sophien Kamoun at The Sainsbury Lab, focuses on the molecular genetics
of interactions between plants and oomycete plant pathogens,
particularly those of the genus Phytophthora.">

