<P><B>[December 11, 2009]</B> <a href="http://www.tsl.ac.uk/profile/sebastian-schornack.asp">Sebastian Schornack</a> co-disovered the amino acid to DNA code which explains how bacterial effectors bind to specific host plant DNA sequences. Read about this work in <a href="http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/1178811" target="_blank">Science</a>.</P>

