<P><B>[January 18-28, 2009]</B> Travel mementoes. Visiting collaborators and friends in Japan and Korea. From left to right: <a href="http://ksg.psc.riken.jp/index.en.html" target="_blank">Ken Shirasu</a> at Riken Plant Science Center, <a href="http://www.ibrc.or.jp/HP-Data2007/500English/rice/main.html" target="_blank">Ryohei Terauchi</a> at the Iwate Biotechnology Research Center, and <a href="http://www.sgn.cornell.edu/community/feature/200405.pl" target="_blank">Doil Choi</a> at Seoul National University.</P>

